Class Node<N extends Comparable<N>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • hw5.Node<N>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Node<N>>

    public class Node<N extends Comparable<N>>
extends Object
implements Comparable<Node<N>>
    Node represents an immutable vertex in a Graph. It includes a String that represents the data of itself.

    Examples of Node include "Node: abc", "Node: def" and so on.
